    "description": "Blue Innovation Co., Ltd. provides inspection, disaster prevention, education, and logistics solutions in Japan and internationally. It offers Blue Earth Platform, a software platform that controls and manages drones and robots for various solutions. The company also provides inspection solutions, including drone power line inspection, inspection and surveying, underwater inspection, sewer inspection, and inspection starter pack, as well as inspection outsourcing plan and robot-based automated patrol inspection; and port solutions, such as drone disaster prevention, automated patrol, and port information management system, as well as portable and fixed drone ports. In addition, it offers education and pilot support solutions comprising plant inspection specialist training course, drone flight log creation and information management service, dedicated drone flight support map service, and compensation; and robot cleaning solutions for offices. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Bunkyo, Japan."
